Interface Visitor<T>

Type Parameters:
T - Return type
All Known Implementing Classes:
CarnivoreMealKit, ConsumableItem, Corpse, Egg, Fish, Fruit, MealKit, VegetarianMealKit, WaterBottle
public interface Visitor<T>
Declare the visit operations for all the types of visitable classes. Part of Visitor Pattern: https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/visitor-design-pattern/
